The paper discusses the difficulty of learning in deep architectures, which is a topic that falls under the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the role of language and communication in aiding the learning process, which falls under the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of neural networks, which falls under the sub-category of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Finally, the paper discusses the optimization difficulty of learning, which falls under the sub-category of software engineering (cs.SD).
